# Meridian Design System

## Color Tokens (always use these, never hardcode other values)

| Purpose | Light | Dark |
|---|---|---|
| Brand / CTA | `#059669` (emerald-600) | same |
| Brand hover | `#047857` (emerald-700) | `#6ee7b7` for text links |
| Body text | `#3f3f46` (zinc-700) | `#e4e4e7` |
| Headings | `#18181b` (zinc-900) | `#fafafa` |
| Muted text | `#71717a` (zinc-500) | `#a1a1aa` |
| Border light | `#e4e4e7` (zinc-200) | `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)` |
| Page background | `white` | `rgb(9 9 11)` (zinc-950) |
| Card background | `white` | `#18181b` (zinc-900) |

CSS variables also available: `--aw-color-primary`, `--aw-color-secondary`, `--aw-color-accent`, `--aw-color-text-default`, `--aw-color-text-muted`.

Tailwind aliases: `text-primary`, `bg-primary`, `text-muted`, `text-default`.

## Typography Scale

```
.eyebrow   → text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase, color #059669
.display   → text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight (-0.03em), color #18181b
.lead      → text-lg leading-relaxed, color #71717a
h1–h4      → color #18181b, letter-spacing -0.02em (set globally)
```

Font family: Inter Variable (`font-sans` / `font-heading`). **Never specify another font.**

## Spacing System

Sections use consistent vertical rhythm — do not invent new padding values:

```
.section        → py-24 lg:py-32 px-6
.section-tight  → py-16 lg:py-24 px-6
```

Containers:
```
.container-narrow → max-w-3xl mx-auto
.container-wide   → max-w-6xl mx-auto
```

For inline/flex alignment: **always use `items-center` on flex rows** that mix text and icons. The most common misalignment bug is forgetting `items-center` on a flex parent.

## Buttons

Use the pre-built classes — do NOT recreate buttons with raw Tailwind:

```html
<!-- Primary CTA -->
<a class="btn btn-primary">Download Free Trial</a>
<a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Download Free Trial</a>

<!-- Secondary -->
<a class="btn btn-secondary">Learn More</a>

<!-- Ghost link -->
<a class="btn-tertiary">See all features →</a>
```

`btn-primary` is `#059669` background, white text, with hover lift.
`btn-secondary` is white/border in light, transparent/border in dark.

## Cards

```html
<div class="card p-6">...</div>
<div class="card card-hover p-6">...</div>  <!-- adds hover lift + green border -->
```

Never use raw `rounded`, `shadow`, `border` combos — always `.card`.

## Dark Mode

All components must work in both modes. Pattern:

```html
<div class="text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
<div class="bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-200 dark:border-white/10">
```

**Or use the named classes** (`.card`, `.lead`, `.display`) which already handle dark mode.

Never add dark mode only for light — if you style something for light, add the dark variant.

## Common Misalignment Fixes

**Icon + text not aligned:**
```html
<!-- ❌ BAD -->
<div class="flex gap-2">
  <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5" />
  <span>Feature text</span>
</div>

<!-- ✅ GOOD -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-2">
  <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0" />
  <span>Feature text</span>
</div>
```

**Horizontal dashes / dividers not aligned with text:**
```html
<!-- ✅ Pattern: flex items-center for rule + label combos -->
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-white/10"></div>
  <span class="text-xs text-zinc-400">or</span>
  <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-white/10"></div>
</div>
```

**Grid columns uneven height / not aligning tops:**
```html
<!-- ✅ For feature grids, always use items-start unless centering is intentional -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 items-start">
```

## Astro Icon Usage

Always import from `astro-icon/components` and use tabler icons:
```astro
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
<Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary" />
```

Available sets: `tabler:*` and `flat-color-icons:*`.
